:: Ask about the smoke {"position":"250,600","size":"100,100"}
"Oh, that?" The shop owner bared lifted his head from the worktable. "That smoke is from where the King commissioned his palace of treasures, Lutai. All of them precious war spoils and gifts from other missionaries are there." 

You glanced again at the direction of the smoke. "Impressive. Do you recall when he started the construction?"

The shop owner pursed his lips yet still did not look up. You get the impression that he is not impressed. "Not a clue. Soon as I started working at this spot the smoke's been there. Are you buying a drink or not?" 

You offered him three cowrie shells for a bowl of rice wine. Parched as you were, you drained the bowl swiftly, and said your thanks.

[[Ask about the temperament of the Shang King]] 
